data.description: BACK ON THE MARKET!!! - Welcome to this charming home in desirable area of Ontario California. This 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom home is ready for its new owners. The home is situated in a suburban neighborhood. With a 6,528 square foot lot, there is plenty of space to create a beautiful landscape. A large entry way invites you to an open living room and large dining area with beautiful laminate wood flooring. You have the kitchen off the dining area. A main floor bedroom and ¾ bath downstairs. In the back of the house is a large office and laundry room. Upstairs leads you to a small landing and 2 bedrooms, one of the bedrooms has been converted into a workspace. There is another ¾ bath and large utility closet on the second floor. Each room has its own cooling wall unit and plenty of ceiling fans to assist in keeping the house cool. This home has updated double pane windows to help with the climate control and solar panels installed to help with the electricity bill. The backyard has plenty of space to entertain guests, start a vegetable garden or any other options, use your own imagination. The garage is equipped with a spacious side workshop. You don’t want to miss out on this gem! Buyer to qualify and transfer solar to their own name. Owner passed away peacefully in the home. Information deemed to be reliable; however Buyers are encouraged to perform their own due diligence to verify all information.
